{"tid":274022,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"「差啲唔記得」呢句有冇問題？","createTime":"2017-06-07T04:14:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-08T17:50:25.000Z","uid":13701,"like":13,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3b7232606d98a868af1e6c0342a35c02f09e46b9","tid":274022,"uid":13701,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T04:14:11.000Z","msg":"講得出呢句通常有個前設：喺未過期嘅情況下突然醒起有野未做<br />\n<br />\n例如你今日要去銀行過數，不過一直唔記得，但過咗一段時間喺突然情況下醒起而且仲趕得切完成，就結果嚟睇你的確係記得完成件事<br />\n<br />\n但係你一直都冇咗回事，只係突然/有個契機令你記起，呢種突發醒起嘅情況其實係咪代表你已經唔記得？<br />\n<br />\n唔記得到記得而且趕得切完成仲係咪「差啲」唔記得？<br />\n<br />\nSor講得1999，希望大家明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇問題，醒起姐係仲記得<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有問題，明明已經唔記得，自己呃自己"},{"pid":"78108645c15a8ec65fcc9b3013973c17a594b7c3","tid":274022,"uid":11161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T04:18:18.000Z","msg":"已經變左口頭嬋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"247602e50bed7a5b239b7c61c76ecf222f31f700","tid":274022,"uid":660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T04:18:30.000Z","msg":"之前見過類似post"},{"pid":"42218fd89a901adf2418797ea93b89a933eddeb1","tid":274022,"uid":1774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T04:23:21.000Z","msg":"應該用好彩記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d417e72110d1e425ac1914144c435fb7b209b4d3","tid":274022,"uid":79207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T04:30:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該用好彩記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好彩記返起感覺上合適啲<br />\n記返起表達到曾經有段時間唔記得左件事<br />\n但係記得似乎強調唔到個變化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ae4918b126d9b8fbf30cf1635c221053e8b8f25","tid":274022,"uid":72186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T04:31:51.000Z","msg":"覺得冇問題 所以負評咗<br />\n利申文盲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"571645522eb005401626355114af2b17769a55b3","tid":274022,"uid":13701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T04:41:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>覺得冇問題 所以負評咗<br />\n利申文盲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n⋯⋯"},{"pid":"ce88e409877f3aa2c59a4f16e7fc2988c9807dd9","tid":274022,"uid":13701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T04:42:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前見過類似post</blockquote><br />\n有冇link或者個post keyword <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbe49093ab5035109f71d2c299d64168461b82bf","tid":274022,"uid":55547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T04:43:37.000Z","msg":"如果件事未過deadline <br />\n你醒起要做 應該可以用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed3777502068d68556e76fd80547d0abae17f21f","tid":274022,"uid":34647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T04:45:21.000Z","msg":"算唔算係悸論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f0603f51bed0b61d54bb438dff871d38a8fe67b","tid":274022,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T04:53:54.000Z","msg":"其實有問題<br />\n依家呢句一般係指你原本唔記得左一件野/事但最後你記得番<br />\neg.我差d唔記得入錢 -》記得番+做得切<br />\n一般人用法係咁<br />\n<br />\n但本身你一開始就已經處於唔記得嘅狀態<br />\n那怕就只有一瞬間唔記得，你都已經脫離[差d]嘅狀態<br />\n<br />\n改番做 差d醒唔起，或者記得番都得"},{"pid":"126382b2b6a578593b3e4a2c164d87fb4fe786c2","tid":274022,"uid":4545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T05:02:27.000Z","msg":"哲學post lm"},{"pid":"367a7c735e40b3d9efb88de9abdb090b91324a12","tid":274022,"uid":13701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T05:05:21.000Z","msg":"如果拆開「差啲」嚟睇，用詞意分析<br />\n差啲仆街姐係未仆<br />\n差啲死姐係未死<br />\n<br />\n差啲其實係帶有僥倖成份而且係就結果而論？咁呢個突然醒起似乎又符合呢兩個條件"},{"pid":"5d6cd8f11bc1d69e759338b9fe6d9ea5e3b5e88e","tid":274022,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T05:06:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>算唔算係悸論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該唔算<br />\n最少唔係真假都有問題"},{"pid":"72a9168052fb7b7e05e78ce8c7d167593ae6ba14","tid":274022,"uid":7555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T05:06:41.000Z","msg":"我反而覺得啲人係當差啲漏咗咁用"},{"pid":"9fe095551c19ec5da8b147e685f9524ffb2948a2","tid":274022,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T05:11:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果拆開「差啲」嚟睇，用詞意分析<br />\n差啲仆街姐係未仆<br />\n差啲死姐係未死<br />\n<br />\n差啲其實係帶有僥倖成份而且係就結果而論？咁呢個突然醒起似乎又符合呢兩個條件</blockquote><br />\n基本上完全係結果論"},{"pid":"aed078761491cec7cfd90ac339d1c5c50b730029","tid":274022,"uid":36245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T15:27:00.000Z","msg":"之前都有諗過<br />\n差啲唔記得 係咪其實係已經唔記得 之後再記起<br />\n但再諗下 我會話係所謂唔記得嘅狀態係「未記得」<br />\n喺要做嘅事發生之前 件事都可以喺腦入面存在消失無限loop<br />\n直到事件發生嘅一刻 腦入面嘅狀態係存在定消失就決定你係咪記得喇<br />\n<br />\n利申: 9up"},{"pid":"83f798f466805e1d47867eb1eca9341cfb16e91c","tid":274022,"uid":15636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T15:32:01.000Z","msg":"最後記得<br />\n姐係記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bad29cb127bf926aa297ceeb7fcd217a24d820ab","tid":274022,"uid":15636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T15:32:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最後記得<br />\n姐係記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以係差啲唔記得<br />\n其實講終於醒起係咪無得拗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b220a0b8d513611fc98f5fdad3609d9120cbe81","tid":274022,"uid":13257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T15:34:15.000Z","msg":"覺得無問題<br />\n<br />\n記得一樣野唔會無時無刻每一秒都記得<br />\n<br />\n差d唔記得，但最後記番，所以都係記得"},{"pid":"f7b66aff18d2b0dcf0395362faaf631bc50c5e80","tid":274022,"uid":86007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T17:13:35.000Z","msg":"我覺得要根據情況 睇下點理解&quot;記唔記得&quot;<br />\n如果係指一段記憶既完整性<br />\n咁&quot;唔記得&quot;就係完全失去對某事物既記憶 而差d唔記得就係形容接近對某事物完全失去記憶 例如某位小學同學<br />\n你已經唔記得佢個樣 但係仲勉強記得名 咁可以話差啲唔記得嗰個人<br />\n<br />\n但係記得去銀行入數個例子  並唔係想講記憶既完整性 重要既係最後結果  所以就算一直唔記得 只要最後記起而入左數 都算係記得 雖然係差d唔記得"},{"pid":"bab5f138747a59b65963c28150c30c4ef66197f3","tid":274022,"uid":23782,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T17:34:20.000Z","msg":"對我黎講，「唔記得」係包埋個結果：唔記得引致無做到/做漏左而形成左一啲影響<br />\n只要喺果啲影響出現之前，記返起要做既事，都叫做記起件事，都可以話自己「差啲唔記得」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該講到1999，無人明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c8c1b79acee10351f245c9930c030389032e12f","tid":274022,"uid":68589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T17:50:25.000Z","msg":"I almost forgot 樓主 is a on9"}]}